<title>USA: Comstock Resources converts pfd shares.</title>
<headline>Comstock Resources converts pfd shares.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1996-09-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Comstock Resources Inc said Monday the holders of its Series 1994 Convertible Preferred Stock converted them into 1.5 million common shares.</p>
<p>The company, which specializes in oil and gas exploration, said it paid quarterly dividends on the preference stock at an annual rate of 9.0 percent before the conversion (about $540,000 per year).</p>
